I'm having suuuuccchhh a hard time deciding on a final template. I should be at 40 by the end of the week barring having to do over-time at work and will be re-speccing from crush into slash. I can't decide between 50 DW/ 50 slash/ rest parry, 50 DW/ 44 slash/ rest parry 44 DW/ 50 slash/ rest parry. I'm not that impressed with how Diamond Slash looks on paper. Dual Shadows looks good now. So I'm inclined toward the 50 DW/ 44 slash but that's giving up a little offensive for a little more defense. Is this really worthwhile? I don't know. I don't know. &lt;bangs head some more&gt;<br>
